{"tid":1795651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱門酒肉臭 路有凍死骨","createTime":"2019-12-24T05:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T08:23:46.000Z","uid":23758,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cabd7833f799e041ace0df3af0bfb25928e37bdb","tid":1795651,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"今晚就有得睇<br />\n睇香港人點樣唱住聖誕膠歌行街、嗌口號<br />\n睇還押、坐監既手足對住四面灰色既牆<br />\n睇過身手足既屋企人對住空盪盪既房"},{"pid":"05bfba10032c8a2f2f378bdb310c55cc2e515117","tid":1795651,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"woho"},{"pid":"43de0a271e1ff55327dc82800fd6556ea721f406","tid":1795651,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05bfba10032c8a2f2f378bdb310c55cc2e515117","tid":1795651,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"woho"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"推文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d860d319f13d156b6547bea012c91d51d7157a56","tid":1795651,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4613f690bdfc1ef136e4dd189737c5f81cd1a49a","tid":1795651,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去大半年，大家既生活都過得好壓抑，好似見到有希望但係又唔知前路候點。有人或者係依大半年同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手離婚，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸又或者有家歸不得，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=fe806e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb78518e0948923403f83698495b649b04328323","tid":1795651,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"練好歌詞未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0518fe0a038e7200b76ce1a51196669fe75a6746","tid":1795651,"uid":23758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:06:41.000Z","msg":"你地根本駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早講好平安夜聖誕去邊到玩"},{"pid":"038583acfd592e41ec8953015f895ed412e1de69","tid":1795651,"uid":37267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cabd7833f799e041ace0df3af0bfb25928e37bdb","tid":1795651,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"今晚就有得睇<br />\n睇香港人點樣唱住聖誕膠歌行街、嗌口號<br />\n睇還押、坐監既手足對住四面灰色既牆<br />\n睇過身手足既屋企人對住空盪盪既房"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得應該要點?有主意咪提出黎"}]}